name: EdobMix
description:
A mix of models I like, I combined this to try and get a better look for my Loras.

It general gives very good images in my opinion.

RevAnimated, Kotosmix, DarelitesFantasyMix

I recommend using DPM++ 2M Karras as the sampler

If you want realism simply add (Realistic:1.5)

Have fun!

If you like this work, try support me, click here >>DONATE<<. TIA!
